data.description: Nestled in the charming community of Pendleton, SC and just minutes from Pendleton Square, Patrick Square and Clemson, 821 Belmina St is a delightful and spacious family home, boasting both brick and vinyl siding, and set on a generous almost 1-acre lot. The property features an estimated living space of 2,900 sq ft and is designed to accommodate a comfortable family lifestyle. The residence comprises 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, providing ample space for family and guests. The interior is elegantly designed with nice hardwood floors, adding warmth and character to the space. The kitchen is well-equipped with abundant cabinet space, a smooth top cook range oven, and a stainless steel double sink, making meal preparation a breeze. The dining room, adorned with French doors, offers an inviting space for formal meals and social gatherings. Additionally, there is a large family room that further extends the living area, also featuring hardwood floors for a cohesive look throughout the home. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, situated upstairs and it also features access to a private upper balcony, offering a peaceful outdoor escape. The primary bathroom has been thoughtfully updated with raised new countertops, dual sinks, a mirror, lights, a shower/jetted tub combo, and ceramic tile flooring, adding a touch of luxury to the space. Two additional bedrooms and another bathroom are located upstairs, while one bedroom and a bathroom are conveniently situated downstairs. The home also includes a bonus room on the main level, adding flexibility to the floor plan. Outside, the wooden deck at the back of the home presents an excellent spot for outdoor living and entertaining. The property includes a 2-car garage attached, a 1-car carport, and almost a full acre of land, offering plenty of space for outdoor activities and gardening. While the home is to be sold "As Is" and may require a bit of TLC, it represents a fantastic opportunity for those looking to make their mark on a lovely family home. The property falls under the Pendleton Schools jurisdiction, adding to its appeal for families with school-aged children. Come see this charming and spacious family home, featuring 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and generous living spaces, both indoors and out! It offers a blend of comfort, space, and potential, making it an ideal choice for a family looking to settle in the delightful Pendleton.
